src package¶

Module contents¶

This package contains all the source code for the app.

It is split into tests and utils subpackages containing the unit tests and utilities for the app respectively.

Subpackages¶

  • src.tests package
  • src.utils package

Submodules¶

src.window_classes module¶

This diagram outlines the design of the window classes describing the inheritance and composition of them:

File of classes representing the windows of the TK GUI.

The windows have been programmed in an object oriented way, each window of the GUI inherits from the abstract window class.

This is an abstract class which provides a framework and base settings for each other GUI window.

class src.window_classes.AbstractWindow(master: Tk)[source]¶

Bases: object

An abstract class to provide a framework for other window classes.
